<form action='@Url.Action("Kontakt","Home")' method='post'>
    <div class="form-group row">
        <label for="name" class="col-3">Name:</label>
        <div class="col-9">
            <input type="text" class="form-control mw-100" name="name" id="name" maxlength="50">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group row">
        <label for="email" class="col-3">E-Mail:</label>
        <div class="col-9">
            <input type="text" class="form-control mw-100" name="email" id="email" maxlength="50">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="message">Nachricht:</label>
        <textarea class="form-control mw-100" name="message" id="message" rows="10" maxlength="3000"></textarea>
    </div>

    <p>
        Hiermit erteile ich gegenüber der Stadt Mosbach meine Einwilligung in die Verarbeitung der
